::FZ/Perndabot::

FZ nods, acknowledging Feline's report. "Allright," he replies, 
looking around.

"Many of your troops havn't stopped firing," he remarkes to Iron 
Raptor, "Mine won't cease fire if they are fired upon."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Perndabot jumps back from the slash, nearly falling to the side when 
Hot Rod's optic blasts hit him. If he wasn't so damaged, he'd tear 
both these bots apart.

He growls, taking several steps back. He hoped that these bots had 
heard Iron Raptor's message.
